data.description: There is so much value in this home. How about a bathroom on every floor in a Beaverdale home? (Basement too!) How about a full two car garage? Beautifully updated kitchen? Check! Walking through the house you notice the pride of ownership. Warmth and light come in through large windows. The master suite occupies the entire second floor and has its own bathroom. Two more bedrooms and a full bath are on the main level. In the fully fenced backyard, you will find a deck, beautiful landscaping, and plenty of shade. See your new home today!
